Key to species of the 
<taxonomicName box="[412,682,1486,1512]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Platypalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hackmani">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[412,682,1486,1512]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="48">Platypalpus hackmani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group from North 
<collectingCountry box="[921,1028,1486,1512]" name="United States of America" pageId="13" pageNumber="48">America</collectingCountry>
